  <trk>
    <name>Circular hike to Flüealp</name>
    <desc>Circular hike along the impressive rock face below the Gemmi Pass to the Flüealp. Cross alpine pastures and reach the impressive stone Flüekapelle. The highlight of the hike is the fantastic panorama.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
